title: 168: The Kinda Positive Episode
description: Just how driven are Sal, Adam & Justin to expose the BS of the fitness industry? So driven that when presented with the challenge of talking about fitness industry positives that they have a hard time staying on track. Raw Fitness Truth cannot be caged.
